  },
  {
    "type": "p",
    "children": [
      {
        "text": "This page provides guidance about getting a business visa for your short-term international business trip."
      }
    ],
    "id": "7J9daYRr5z"
  },
  {
    "type": "p",
    "children": [
      {
        "text": "\u00a0"
      }
    ],
    "id": "OcZBYAwt_P"
  },
  {
    "type": "p",
    "children": [
      {
        "text": "\u2139\ufe0f "
      },
      {
        "text": "remarque: ",
        "bold": true
      },
      {
        "text": " Getting a business visa is just one key step international business travelers need to consider. Review the "
      },
      {
        "type": "a",
        "target": "_blank",
        "url": "https://w.amazon.com/bin/view/Immigration/ShortTermTravelResources/Checklist/",
        "children": [
          {
            "text": "International Short-Term Travel Checklist"
          }
        ],
        "id": "",
        "anchorId": ""
      },
      {
        "text": " for an overview of steps travelers should take prior to departure."
      }
    ],
    "id": "RRunrlhEou"
  },
  {
    "type": "p",
    "children": [
      {
        "text": "\u00a0"
      }
    ],
    "id": "CtZPxj5A2V"
  },
  {
    "type": "h2",
    "children": [
      {
        "text": "Overview"
      }
    ],
    "id": "0YLmY6x7PP"
  },
  {
    "type": "p",
    "children": [
      {
        "text": "At Amazon, you can usually complete your own business visa application using self-service (unless noted otherwise below). You must carry any required documents when transiting through a country, including a transit visa, visitor\u2019s visa, or business visa."
      }
    ],
    "id": "6l9lrxD9D9"
  },
  {
    "type": "p",
    "children": [
      {
        "text": "\u00a0"
      }
    ],
    "id": "4KJ6mle5yl"
  },
  {
    "type": "h2",
    "children": [
      {
        "text": "Get a pre-travel immigration assessment"
      }
    ],
    "id": "M7tqjLhdfW"
  },
  {
    "type": "p",
    "children": [
      {
        "text": "If you will travel to perform productive (hands-on) work, you may need more than a business or visitor visa. Amazon\u2019s Go Work tool will provide you a fast, easy-to-use assessment to determine the visa requirements for your travel. Visit the "
      },
      {
        "type": "a",
        "target": "_blank",
        "url": "https://w.amazon.com/bin/view/Immigration/ShortTermTravelResources/",
        "children": [
          {
            "text": "Short-Term Travel Resources wiki"
          }
        ],
        "id": "",
        "anchorId": ""
      },
      {
        "text": " to get your Go Work assessment."
      }
    ],
    "id": "f4LNGkSNNg"
  },
  {
    "type": "p",
    "children": [
      {
        "text": "\u00a0"
      }
    ],
    "id": "Mnupx30oA9"
  },
  {
    "type": "h2",
    "children": [
      {
        "text": "Get an invitation letter"
      }
    ],
    "id": "H2lHvAgTb1"
  },
  {
    "type": "p",
    "children": [
      {
        "text": "If you need an invitation letter from Amazon for your short-term international travel, refer to "
      },
      {
        "type": "a",
        "target": null,
        "url": "https://inside.hr.amazon.dev/content/inside/language-master/en/employment/your-career-global/invitation-letters.html",
        "children": [
          {
            "text": "Invitation Letters"
          }
        ],
        "id": "",
        "anchorId": ""
      },
      {
        "text": "."
      }
    ],
    "id": "KnpxW8Q8iz"
  },
  {
    "type": "p",
    "children": [
      {
        "text": "\u00a0"
      }
    ],
    "id": "IwBZApZmTk"
  },
  {
    "type": "h2",
    "children": [
      {
        "text": "Apply for a business visa"
      }
    ],
    "id": "Y3d4cahr3g"
  },
  {
    "type": "p",
    "children": [
      {
        "text": "In most cases, business visa applications are self-serve. In some regions, Amazon provides tools and other support to travelers. Some countries have more than one option for support. If you do not see a country listed below, you can choose your own vendor to obtain your business visa."
      }
    ],
    "id": "FOxeVw4rkT"
  },
  {
    "type": "p",
    "children": [
      {
        "text": "You can seek reimbursement under Amazon\u2019s "
      },
      {
        "type": "a",
        "target": "_blank",
        "url": "https://w.amazon.com/bin/viewrev/Concur_Global_Expense/#Non-Reimbursable)",
        "children": [
          {
            "text": "expense policy"
          }
        ],
        "id": "",
        "anchorId": ""
      },
      {
        "text": " for any business visa costs you incur. To request reimbursement, select "
      },
      {
        "text": "Start a Report",
        "bold": true
      },
      {
        "text": " within "
      },
      {
        "type": "a",
        "target": "_blank",
        "url": "https://expenses.corp.amazon.com/",
        "children": [
          {
            "text": "SAP Concur"
          }
        ],
        "id": "",
        "anchorId": ""
      },
      {
        "text": ".\u00a0 For expense type, select "
      },
      {
        "text": "Other",
        "bold": true
      },
      {
        "text": ", then "
      },
      {
        "text": "Miscellaneous",
        "bold": true
      },
      {
        "text": ", and then "
      },
      {
        "text": "Visa Fees",
        "bold": true
      },
      {
        "text": "."
      }
    ],
    "id": "Q5epLKEaJh"
  },
  {
    "type": "p",
    "children": [
      {
        "text": "\u00a0"
      }
    ],
    "id": "jWq6Wu8vHW"
  },
  {
    "type": "p",
    "children": [
      {
        "text": "\u2139\ufe0f "
      },
      {
        "text": "remarque: ",
        "bold": true
      },
      {
        "text": " If your departure and arrival countries aren\u2019t supported below, you can click on\u00a0"
      },
      {
        "text": "Don\u2019t reside in one of these countries?",
        "bold": true
      },
      {
        "text": "\u00a0at the bottom of the "
      },
      {
        "type": "a",
        "target": null,
        "url": "https://cibtvisas.co.uk/amazon-global-splash?login=201811",
        "children": [
          {
            "text": "CIBT visas page"
          }
        ],
        "id": "",
        "anchorId": ""
      },
      {
        "text": " for guidance. \u00a0"
      }
    ],
    "id": "kRRwJCEpWG"
  },
  {
    "type": "p",
    "children": [
      {
        "text": "\u00a0"
      }
    ],
    "id": "g0abHW1xYP"
  },
  {
    "type": "h3",
    "children": [
      {
        "text": "Americas"
      }
    ],
    "id": "wAA7Zhbv61"
  },
  {
    "type": "p",
    "children": [
      {
        "text": "If you are based in the United States, you can engage "
      },
      {
        "type": "a",
        "target": "_blank",
        "url": "https://visawolf.com/amazon-visa-intake-sheet/",
        "children": [
          {
            "text": "Visa Wolf"
          }
        ],
        "id": "",
        "anchorId": ""
      },
      {
        "text": " for support. If you need a business visa, Visa Wolf will prepare and submit your application."
      }
    ],
    "id": "ziYVi5abLb"
  },
  {
    "type": "p",
    "children": [
      {
        "text": "If you are based in Brazil, Canada, Mexico, or the United States, you can use CIBT\u2019s "
      },
      {
        "type": "a",
        "target": "_blank",
        "url": "https://cibtvisas.co.uk/amazon-global-splash?login=201811",
        "children": [
          {
            "text": "Amazon Global Visa Support Centre"
          }
        ],
        "id": "",
        "anchorId": ""
      },
      {
        "text": ". If you need a business visa, CIBT will prepare and submit your application."
      }
    ],
    "id": "KaiezQOhcz"
  },
  {
    "type": "p",
    "children": [
      {
        "text": "If you live in a different country in the Americas, you can refer to the "
      },
      {
        "type": "a",
        "target": "_blank",
        "url": "https://cibtvisas.co.uk/amazon-global-splash?login=201811",
        "children": [
          {
            "text": "CIBT visas page"
          }
        ],
        "id": "",
        "anchorId": ""
      },
      {
        "text": " and click on the "
      },
      {
        "text": "Don\u2019t reside in one of these countries? ",
        "bold": true
      },
      {
        "text": "button at the bottom of the page for guidance."
      }
    ],
    "id": "0VP39Ns0kS"
  },
  {
    "type": "p",
    "children": [
      {
        "text": ""
      }
    ],
    "id": "AxX0K7YjBX"
  },
  {
    "type": "h3",
    "children": [
      {
        "text": "Asia Pacific (APAC)"
      }
    ],
    "id": "0DDq3qqCX-"
  },
  {
    "type": "p",
    "children": [
      {
        "text": "If you are traveling to China or Indonesia, Amazon Immigration recommends you seek help from one of Amazon\u2019s sponsored immigration service providers. Submit an immigration\u00a0"
      },
      {
        "type": "a",
        "target": "_blank",
        "url": "https://form.asana.com/?k=kfSdQzYDlTML03aIrcju8g&d=8442528107068",
        "children": [
          {
            "text": "initiation request"
          }
        ],
        "id": "",
        "anchorId": ""
      },
      {
        "text": " to get started\u00a0(link requires Amazon network or active VPN connection)."
      }
    ],
    "id": "kXBlQqoDd7"
  },
  {
    "type": "p",
    "children": [
      {
        "text": "If you are based in India, Japan, Philippines, or China, CWT can assist you. Review "
      },
      {
        "type": "a",
        "target": null,
        "url": "https://w.amazon.com/bin/view/TravelAndEvents/India/",
        "children": [
          {
            "text": "India"
          }
        ],
        "id": "",
        "anchorId": ""
      },
      {
        "text": ", "
      },
      {
        "type": "a",
        "target": null,
        "url": "https://inside.amazon.com/en/MyWorkplace/JPTravel/Pages/default.aspx",
        "children": [
          {
            "text": "Japan"
          }
        ],
        "id": "",
        "anchorId": ""
      },
      {
        "text": ", and "
      },
      {
        "type": "a",
        "target": null,
        "url": "https://inside.amazon.com/en/MyWorkplace/CNTravel/Pages/default.aspx",
        "children": [
          {
            "text": "China"
          }
        ],
        "id": "",
        "anchorId": ""
      },
      {
        "text": " resources to get started. For the Philippines, "
      },
      {
        "type": "a",
        "target": "_blank",
        "url": "mailto:documentation@mycwt.com.ph?subject=Philippines%20Business%20Visa",
        "children": [
          {
            "text": "email CWT"
          }
        ],
        "id": "",
        "anchorId": ""
      },
      {
        "text": "."
      }
    ],
    "id": "N2gdBV8Z3e"
  },
  {
    "type": "p",
    "children": [
      {
        "text": "If you are based in Singapore or China, you can also use CIBT\u2019s "
      },
      {
        "type": "a",
        "target": "_blank",
        "url": "https://cibtvisas.co.uk/amazon-global-splash?login=201811",
        "children": [
          {
            "text": "Amazon Global Visa Support Centre"
          }
        ],
        "id": "",
        "anchorId": ""
      },
      {
        "text": ". If you need a business visa, CIBT will prepare and submit your application."
      }
    ],
    "id": "PTFJwU5isQ"
  },
  {
    "type": "p",
    "children": [
      {
        "text": "If you live in a different country in APAC, you can refer to the "
      },
      {
        "type": "a",
        "target": "_blank",
        "url": "https://cibtvisas.co.uk/amazon-global-splash?login=201811",
        "children": [
          {
            "text": "CIBT visas page"
          }
        ],
        "id": "",
        "anchorId": ""
      },
      {
        "text": " and click on the "
      },
      {
        "text": "Don\u2019t reside in one of these countries?",
        "bold": true
      },
      {
        "text": "\u00a0button at the bottom of the page for guidance."
      }
    ],
    "id": "k9aIz9cXWV"
