  },
  {
    "type": "h3",
    "children": [
      {
        "text": "Europe"
      }
    ],
    "id": "JlsKm4ns_Z"
  },
  {
    "type": "p",
    "children": [
      {
        "text": "If you are based in Austria, Belgium, Denmark, France, Finland, Germany, the Netherlands, Norway, Spain, Sweden, Switzerland, or the United Kingdom, use CIBT\u2019s "
      },
      {
        "type": "a",
        "target": "_blank",
        "url": "https://cibtvisas.co.uk/amazon-global-splash?login=201811",
        "children": [
          {
            "text": "Amazon Global Visa Support Centre"
          }
        ],
        "id": "",
        "anchorId": ""
      },
      {
        "text": ". If you need a business visa, CIBT will prepare and submit your application. CIBT will charge you directly, and you can seek reimbursement from Amazon."
      }
    ],
    "id": "fV6-we6QUd"
  },
  {
    "type": "p",
    "children": [
      {
        "text": "If you live in a different country in Europe, you can refer to the "
      },
      {
        "type": "a",
