  {
    "type": "h3",
    "children": [
      {
        "text": "Middle East"
      }
    ],
    "id": "Vxi5KXdyHv"
  },
  {
    "type": "p",
    "children": [
      {
        "text": "If you are traveling to Bahrain, Egypt, Jordan, Kuwait, Saudi Arabia, Turkey, or the United Arab Emirates, Amazon Immigration recommends you seek help from one of Amazon\u2019s sponsored immigration service providers. Submit an immigration "
      },
      {
        "type": "a",
        "target": "_blank",
        "url": "https://form.asana.com/?k=kfSdQzYDlTML03aIrcju8g&d=8442528107068",
        "children": [
          {
            "text": "initiation request"
          }
        ],
        "id": "",
        "anchorId": ""
      },
      {
        "text": " to get started\u00a0(link requires Amazon network or active VPN connection)."
      }
    ],
    "id": "4GyqfMFVC7"
  },
  {
    "type": "p",
    "children": [
      {
        "children": [
          {
            "text": "If you are based in the United Arab Emirates, Bahrain, Kuwait, Jordan, and Egypt: CWT can also assist you. For UAE, Bahrain, and Kuwait, review the resources on our "
          }
        ],
        "type": "p",
        "id": "PXGgRbGB4D"
      },
      {
        "type": "dam-file",
        "nodeId": "b75385e1-5a90-4df4-820f-c031d909d554",
        "children": [
          {
            "text": "UAE"
          }
        ],
        "title": "UAE",
        "id": "-tZLDFHMiS"
      },
      {
        "children": [
          {
            "text": " page. For Egypt, review the resources on our "
          }
        ],
        "type": "p",
        "id": "efSlivi_Ou"
      },
      {
        "type": "dam-file",
        "nodeId": "6adf5faa-3ed5-456b-a998-68c496b600de",
        "children": [
          {
            "text": "Egypt"
          }
        ],
        "title": "Egypt",
        "id": "bewju6rAo6"
      },
      {
        "children": [
          {
            "text": " page. For Jordan, "
          },
          {
            "type": "a",
            "target": "_blank",
            "url": "mailto:res1@mycwt.jo?subject=Jordan%20Business%20Visa",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "email\u00a0CWT"
              }
            ],
            "id": "",
            "anchorId": ""
          },
          {
            "text": "."
          }
        ],
        "type": "p",
        "id": "9LSn6_tIBC"
      }
    ],
    "id": "l9Zw2mQIwy"
  },
  {
